# Local development only
# Do not commit real values
# TEAM_DOMAIN and POLICY_AUD are only required after you configure Cloudflare Access.
# API_KEY is optional and only applies to /api and /api/* automation.
# PASSWORD_SESSION_SECRET signs short-lived password-gate sessions. Use a unique random value in production.
# For GitHub auto-deploy or the Deploy Button, set production values in Cloudflare Variables and Secrets instead of local files.
# TEAM_DOMAIN and POLICY_AUD are text values; API_KEY and PASSWORD_SESSION_SECRET should be treated as secrets.

TEAM_DOMAIN=https://your-team.cloudflareaccess.com
POLICY_AUD=replace-with-your-access-aud
API_KEY=replace-with-a-local-admin-api-key
PASSWORD_SESSION_SECRET=replace-with-a-random-session-secret
